feed.status: AIUCBEF Congrats Newly elected Team of our CHHATTISGARH unit

feed.name: AIUCBEF
feed.status: Our CHATTISGARH unit' s Third triennial conference ,held on 24 th April was a stupendous success. Highlight of the conference was enthusiastic involvement of huge number of young comrades.Com.Ashok Nagrale and Com.Shirish were reelected as President and General Secretary with a team of large number of young comrades as officebearers and Committe members. AIUCBEF WISH THE TEAM ALL SUCCESS AND CONGRATULATES OUR CHATTISGARH UNIT.

feed.name: AIBEA this day 21st April
feed.status: 1946 - AIBEA Foundation Conference: Constitution adopted. K C Neogy and Ramesh Chakraborti elected President and General Secretary. 2010 - UFBU meets FM on Pension Option issue. 1980 - 3rd Bipartite Residual issues settled.

feed.name: AIBEAs Birth Day today
feed.status: 1935 - Com. R D Trivedi, former Vice President, AIBEA (date of birth). 1946 - Foundation Day of AIBEA. 1953 - Sastri Award published. 1960 - XI Conference of AIBEA. Com. Tarakeswar Chakraborti elected as Assistant Secretary for the first time at Hyderabad. Roshan Ali Khan, Mayor of Hyderabad inaugurates. 1971 - Massive AIBEA Silver Jubilee celebrations. Veterans and several Ministers participate. AIBEA Flag adopted. 1987 - Prabhat Parvana Trade Union Training Institute inaugurated at Madras.
